<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[١٨٣٨ - د ل هـ]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>دلَّهَ يُدلِّه، تَدْلِيهًا، فهو مُدَلِّه، والمفعول مُدَلَّه <span class="c2">(للمتعدِّي)</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">• دلَّه الحبُّ الشَّخصَ:</span> حَيَّره وأَدْهَشَه وأَذهبَ فؤادَه <span class="c1">"دلَّهه العِشْقُ/ الحزنُ"</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>